{"id": 1037, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得吃什么食物表示你和别人已经很熟悉了？", "description": "好朋友大概就是一边吃蛋卷一边掉渣还能愉快聊天的人吧。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6383, "comment_count": 72, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130106agS9sItRPA37dpmE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-07T01:00:10Z", "questions": [{"id": 918, "title": "你觉得吃什么食物表示你和别人已经很熟悉了？", "content": "你觉得吃什么食物表示你们已经很熟悉了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 84135, "content": "难度系数很高的：芒果、大块的西瓜", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125850T1Nd2WGlHwfunV6Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84143, "content": "容易掉汤汁/渣的：汤、蛋卷、小笼包", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125850w82I4mQtrbTysoMJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84150, "content": "容易发出声音的：拉面、螺丝、粥", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125850bXekCJzGlh1rKsmU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84155, "content": "需要自己用手包着吃的：生菜包烤肉、酥饼包烤鸭", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183304gGyEwWLK3IH8TRre.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84156, "content": "吃起来龇牙咧嘴的：猪蹄、鸭翅鸡翅", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125934h76GMoeXBjfkPsAz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84158, "content": "用筷子很难夹起来的：山药、过桥米线 ", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125851IwlPOq2r5gKXe3yL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84159, "content": "有刺激性气味的：榴莲、螺蛳粉、臭豆腐", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183312P7vJs58VHqbEXy2S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 84160, "content": "吃相有待商榷的：烤全羊、小龙虾", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125927GOhnBPe6lZkHCSR3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}